{"words":[{"word":"star","count":7},{"word":"around","count":3},{"word":"said","count":3},{"word":"lost","count":2},{"word":"sing","count":2},{"word":"protect","count":2},{"word":"already","count":2},{"word":"i'll","count":2},{"word":"better","count":2},{"word":"mom's","count":1},{"word":"special","count":1},{"word":"treasure","count":1},{"word":"light","count":1},{"word":"kept","count":1},{"word":"darkness","count":1},{"word":"away","count":1},{"word":"looked","count":1},{"word":"everyone","count":1},{"word":"sea","count":1},{"word":"liked","count":1},{"word":"mommy","count":1},{"word":"plays","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"represents","count":1},{"word":"hope","count":1},{"word":"keep","count":1},{"word":"safe","count":1},{"word":"n-now","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"anyone","count":1},{"word":"anymore","count":1},{"word":"b-but","count":1},{"word":"dangerous","count":1},{"word":"saved","count":1},{"word":"mom","count":1},{"word":"cause","count":1},{"word":"trouble","count":1},{"word":"others","count":1},{"word":"okay","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"rest","count":1},{"word":"star's","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"thank","count":1},{"word":"male","count":1},{"word":"mister","count":1},{"word":"female","count":1},{"word":"miss","count":1},{"word":"definitely","count":1},{"word":"actually","count":1},{"word":"feeling","count":1},{"word":"ahead","count":1},{"word":"opera","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"bustle","count":1},{"word":"outside","count":1},{"word":"bed","count":1},{"word":"figured","count":1},{"word":"preparing","count":1},{"word":"show","count":1},{"word":"girl","count":1},{"word":"purple","count":1},{"word":"hair","count":1},{"word":"wanted","count":1},{"word":"use","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"really","count":1},{"word":"shiny","count":1},{"word":"north","count":1},{"word":"pegasus","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"beats","count":1},{"word":"together","count":1},{"word":"wonderful","count":1},{"word":"ship","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"I lost Mom's special treasure...","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000},{"text":"The light from the star kept the darkness away. It looked after everyone when we were at sea...","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000},{"text":"We liked to sing around it, just like Mommy did in her plays.","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000},{"text":"She always said the star represents hope. It would keep me safe, and protect those around me.","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000},{"text":"N-now I've lost it and it can't protect anyone anymore...","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000},{"text":"B-But it's too dangerous out there... You already saved me... And Mom said I shouldn't cause so much trouble for others.","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000},{"text":"Okay... I'll be good and rest.","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000},{"text":"The star... The star's back!","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000},{"text":"Oh, thank you, {Male=mister;Female=miss}! Now the star is here, I'll definitely get better!","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000},{"text":"I'm actually feeling much better already!","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000},{"text":"Go ahead. It's for the opera, right? I heard so much bustle outside while I was in bed. I figured they were preparing for a show.","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000},{"text":"The girl with the purple hair said she wanted to use something really shiny as the North Star in <i>Pegasus</i>. Well, nothing beats this star!","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000},{"text":"Now we can all sing together around the star again. It will be wonderful, just like it was back on the ship!","quest_name":"Starry is the Night","quest_id":154000000}]}